    <h1>Vanity Metrics</h1>
    <p class="description">Numbers that look impressive in a dashboard but <strong>don't correlate with revenue, retention, or real growth</strong>. Understanding which of your KPIs are vanity metrics is the first step to building a marketing function that actually compounds.</p>
